../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:74:The central gamble is that a small family of invariant tensor observables can meaningfully constrain the full pressure-Hessian contribution, including harmonic far-field freedom. That is a severe compression step, and the chain does not really justify why it should work beyond hopeful analogy.
