+
+## Output Requirements
+
+Write:
+
+- `REPORT.md`
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md`
+
+Keep the conclusion endpoint-first. The goal is to freeze one theorem ledger,
+not to rescue the tensor branch rhetorically.
