+  suitable-weak / Leray-Hopf plus LEI, CKN/Lin epsilon-regularity contradiction
+  package with the live bad term fixed as `I_p^far`.
+- `full stretching control` and free-standing `pressure-Hessian/strain defect
+  control` must be rejected as Step-1 endpoint drift.
