+  receptionist note, Explorations 001 and 002, Step-001 far-field obstruction
+  result, and the far-field / obstruction-screening library notes; then rewrote
+  the admission rules directly against the frozen full pairing rather than
+  abstract tensor language.
+
+- Outcome:
+  succeeded
+
+- Final Step-009 verdict:
+  `endpoint frozen, proceed to prior-art and packaging screening`
+
+- Frozen rule 1:
+  [INFERRED] Same-scale unconstrained exterior or harmonic freedom is immediate
+  failure specifically when, after full harmonic accounting and any required
+  localization debt, the full reconstructed `I_p^far` pairing still carries an
+  uncontrolled same-scale affine-or-higher harmonic remainder, so no positive-
+  margin coefficient shrinkage on the full pairing is proved.
+
+- Frozen rule 2:
+  [INFERRED] Tao sensitivity is mandatory but not sufficient:
+  a candidate must fail the relevant averaged-model comparison, but that only
+  counts if the same candidate also lowers the effective coefficient in the
+  frozen full-pairing estimate for `I_p^far`.
