 # History of Report Summaries
 
 Exploration summaries will be appended here as they land.
+
+## Exploration 001
+
+# Exploration 001 Summary
+
+- Goal:
+  freeze the smallest serious theorem-endpoint menu for `step-009`, using only
+  local repository materials, and decide whether run-006 has one exact theorem
+  endpoint / contradiction line or only endpoint-adjacent tensor bottleneck
+  language.
+
+- What I tried:
+  read the Step-009 goal, `decision-013`, `decision-014`, `CHAIN.md`, the
+  run-006 chain files (`winning-chain`, `final-decider`, `selected`,
+  `judgments`, `attacks`, `planner`, `selector`), the inherited far-field
+  obstruction packet from `step-001`, the framework-endpoint freeze notes, and
+  the CKN/Lin proof-architecture files. I also checked whether the run-006
+  target phrases ever become a literal inequality, continuation criterion, or
+  defect identity on disk.
+
+- Outcome:
+  succeeded.
+
+- One key takeaway:
+  the local record supports exactly one real Step-1 theorem ledger:
+  the inherited suitable-weak / Leray-Hopf plus LEI, CKN/Lin epsilon-regularity
+  contradiction package, with the live bad term fixed as the far-field pressure
+  pairing `I_p^far`; the run-006 tensor targets are not independent theorem
+  endpoints unless they act on that same coefficient.
+
+- Primary recommendation:
+  freeze Step 1 on the inherited local-energy / epsilon-regularity
+  contradiction line with one exact cash-out inequality on `I_p^far`. Treat
+  pressure-Hessian language as admissible only if it yields estimate-level
+  action on that same live coefficient.
+
+## Exploration 002
+
+# Exploration 002 Summary
+
+- Goal:
+  stress-test the cash-out, progress currency, and minimum threshold for the
+  best Step-009 endpoint candidate, staying estimate-level and tied to the
+  inherited live far-field pressure pairing.
+
+- What I tried:
+  read the Step-009 goal, the receptionist narrowing, `step-001` far-field
+  obstruction results, the Step-001 reconstruction and Tao-gate reports, the
+  far-field obstruction factual notes, the obstruction-screening meta notes,
+  the exact-rewrite same-protocol screening note, `CHAIN.md`, `run-006`
+  chain/judgment files, and the earlier Step-009 endpoint-menu freeze report.
+  I tested each candidate currency and threshold against the fixed live pairing
+  `I_p^far` and against the requirement that later reconstruction and
+  localization debt cannot erase the gain.
+
+- Outcome:
+  succeeded.
+
+- One key takeaway:
+  the only non-cosmetic Step-1 freeze supported by the repository is a
+  full-pairing inequality on `I_p^far` whose progress currency is a genuinely
+  smaller effective far-field coefficient; harmonic-moment cancellation counts
+  only if it is the mechanism producing that same coefficient shrinkage.
+
+- Recommended threshold:
+  `[PROPOSED]`
+  freeze a uniform positive-margin net shrinkage after later reconstruction and
+  any required localization debt:
+  `C_far,eff(k) <= (1-delta) ||u||_{L^2}^2 / r_k^3`
+  for some `delta > 0`, or an equivalent full-pairing estimate with the same
+  net margin.
+
+## Exploration 003
+
+# Exploration 003 Summary
+
+- Goal:
+  freeze the exact same-scale failure rule, the exact Tao rule, and the final
+  Step-009 verdict for the already-frozen `I_p^far` endpoint ledger.
+
+- What I tried:
+  read the Step-009 goal, active chain, controller decision, run-006 judgment,
+  receptionist note, Explorations 001 and 002, Step-001 far-field obstruction
+  result, and the far-field / obstruction-screening library notes; then rewrote
+  the admission rules directly against the frozen full pairing rather than
+  abstract tensor language.
+
+- Outcome:
+  succeeded
+
+- Final Step-009 verdict:
+  `endpoint frozen, proceed to prior-art and packaging screening`
+
+- Frozen rule 1:
+  [INFERRED] Same-scale unconstrained exterior or harmonic freedom is immediate
+  failure specifically when, after full harmonic accounting and any required
+  localization debt, the full reconstructed `I_p^far` pairing still carries an
+  uncontrolled same-scale affine-or-higher harmonic remainder, so no positive-
+  margin coefficient shrinkage on the full pairing is proved.
+
+- Frozen rule 2:
+  [INFERRED] Tao sensitivity is mandatory but not sufficient:
+  a candidate must fail the relevant averaged-model comparison, but that only
+  counts if the same candidate also lowers the effective coefficient in the
+  frozen full-pairing estimate for `I_p^far`.
