 # Strategizer Reasoning
 
 The strategizer will append its execution reasoning here.
+
+## Iteration 1
+
+- Read `GOAL.md`, `state.json`, `CHAIN.md`, `CHAIN-HISTORY.md`,
+  `decision-013.md`, `decision-014.md`, `run-006/winning-chain.md`,
+  `run-006/final-decider.md`, and `step-008/RESULTS.md`.
+- Queried the receptionist before launching any new exploration, as required.
+- Receptionist result: the live branch is the new run-006 pressure-Hessian
+  chain; the smallest serious menu is
+  `full stretching control`,
+  `pressure-Hessian/strain defect control`,
+  `cancellation of affine-and-higher harmonic moments`;
+  and the strongest locally supported endpoint-shaped cash-out is still the
+  old far-field coefficient ledger from `step-001`, not a free-floating tensor
+  endpoint.
+- Working hypothesis for Exploration 001:
+  verify whether the only coherent theorem endpoint is the inherited local-
+  energy / epsilon-regularity contradiction line with a sharpened estimate on
+  the live far-field pairing, and reject broader endpoint talk that is really
+  just tensor packaging.
+- Working hypothesis for Exploration 002:
+  if the far-field coefficient-reduction ledger is the best freeze target, then
+  the correct progress currency is a quantified reduction of the live nonlocal
+  coefficient (or exact cancellation of the moment family generating it), and
+  the minimum threshold must be a genuine positive-margin reduction that still
+  matters after later reconstruction and localization debt.
+
+### Exploration 001 outcome
+
+- Exploration 001 confirmed the endpoint menu is one actual theorem ledger plus
+  mechanism subcandidates, not several equal theorem endpoints.
+- The only exact theorem endpoint locally frozen on disk is the inherited
+  suitable-weak / Leray-Hopf plus LEI, CKN/Lin epsilon-regularity contradiction
+  package with the live bad term fixed as `I_p^far`.
+- `full stretching control` and free-standing `pressure-Hessian/strain defect
+  control` must be rejected as Step-1 endpoint drift.
+- The remaining live positive-looking option is endpoint-attached mechanism
+  language:
+  a pressure-Hessian defect identity or harmonic-moment cancellation statement
+  that shrinks the same live coefficient.
+
+### Exploration 002 outcome
+
+- Exploration 002 confirmed that the exact cash-out must stay on the same full
+  pairing `I_p^far`; no free-standing tensor identity or local surrogate is
+  enough.
+- The correct progress currency is quantified reduction of the specified
+  nonlocal remainder, i.e. shrinkage of the effective coefficient on the live
+  far-field pairing.
+- The strongest Step-1 threshold shape supported locally is a uniform
+  positive-margin net shrinkage after later reconstruction and localization
+  debt:
+  `C_far,eff(k) <= (1-delta) ||u||_{L^2}^2 / r_k^3`
+  for some `delta > 0`, or an equivalent full-pairing estimate with the same
+  net margin.
+- Weaker thresholds are ruled out:
+  constants are already killed, generic harmonic regularity is Tao-compatible,
+  and any partial gain that leaves the full-pairing coefficient unchanged is
+  cosmetic by the same-protocol rule.
+
+### Exploration 003 outcome
+
+- Exploration 003 confirmed the endpoint setup survives Step 1 narrowly enough
+  to proceed.
+- Same-scale unconstrained exterior/harmonic freedom has now been frozen in
+  exact endpoint language:
+  if after full harmonic accounting and any required localization debt the full
+  reconstructed `I_p^far` pairing still carries an uncontrolled same-scale
+  affine-or-higher harmonic remainder, the branch fails immediately because it
+  has not proved positive-margin coefficient shrinkage on the full pairing.
+- The Tao rule has now been frozen in exact endpoint language:
+  a candidate must fail the relevant averaged-model comparison, but that only
+  counts if it also lowers the effective coefficient in the frozen full-pairing
+  estimate for `I_p^far`.
+- Step verdict can therefore be written as
